# ---------- AWSIM map debug outputs ----------
# `--save-ego-debug-pcd` writes this companion file showing the points the
# vehicle-self filter rejected. Regenerable, so don't commit it.
map/**/ego_returns.pcd

# ---------- TM99 sample blobs (~90 GB each) ----------
# Fetched on demand by data/TM99_uphill/download.sh — too large for git/LFS.
data/TM99_uphill/raw.db3

# ---------- generated MCAP bags (anywhere in the repo) ----------
# Every .mcap is a derived artefact — `cleaned_tf.mcap` is regenerable from
# `raw.db3` via convert_db3_to_mcap.py, and any test slices written to
# /tmp/... or under data/ are likewise reproducible. Never commit them.
*.mcap
